title: Snap-N-Store CD Storage Box, 13.25 x 5.125 x 5.125 Inches, Black (SNS01521)
description: Snap-N-Store collapsible storage products offer tasteful storage solutions that fit with most any home or office décor. With elegant chrome accents and sharp high-gloss or leather-like embossed finishes, this range is so attractive that you can keep them right out in the open. The Snap-N-Store CD Storage Box lets you store up to 165 CDs. This attractive box holds up to 30 CDs in full jewel cases, 60 CDs in slim cases, and 165 discs in CD sleeves. It is constructed with leather-like PVC laminate for durability and features functional chrome accents which provide stylish reinforcement. This box ships and stores flat, but snaps together in seconds for use. The chrome card holder is perfect for labeling your contents for quick and easy reference. Snap-N-Store products are amazingly sturdy, and are also kind to the environment, since they contain 50 percent post-consumer recycled content. Get Snap-N-Store for convenient, economical and fashionable storage!
